#: ../../user/how-to-guides/how-to-use-disposables.rst:232
#: 12ba35903eea4c5a8e0dc2a627a0e960
msgid "Customizing disposables"
msgstr ""

#: ../../user/how-to-guides/how-to-use-disposables.rst:235
#: 160bb0a8ae07417d928780697c5d8ae3
msgid ""
"You can change the template used to generate the disposables, and change "
"settings used in the disposable savefile. These changes will be reflected"
" in every new disposable based on that template. Full instructions can be"
" found :doc:`here </user/advanced-topics/disposable-customization>`."
msgstr ""

